      "comment": "OUR ULTIMATE GRACY NZ (3) turned in a strong effort at her latest appearance over 2180m at Terang, beaten 2.5 metres into fourth after being handy in the run. Has the benefit of a good draw. Won't find this any harder and she can test this line-up. FERRIGNO (4) made a nice return at his latest appearance two weeks ago, finishing 9 metres away in second over 1609m at Cranbourne. His last-start form is good enough to win a race of this calibre. RANGER RICK NZ (5) has been thereabouts of late and is a great chance to break through. Good effort last time out when he finished fourth at Melton over 1720m. WICKED MITZI (2) is in the mix following a fourth at her first run back over 1720m at Melton.",
